  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Meteospasmyl® in Irritable Bowel Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of Meteospasmyl® in Irritable Bowel Syndrome. a 4-Week, Multicentre, Double-Blind, Randomised, Placebo-Controlled Phase IV Trial</official_title>
